    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i've heard it's just an herbal supplement so it shouldn't be as intense as actual drugs. i'm not planning on taking a ton, just like one capsule a day to see if it helps. do you really think it's that big of a deal if it's just a little bit? i really can't deal with a doctor's appointment right now with all this studying",
